summary.span: 为动态定义的泛型类型和方法定义并创建泛型类型参数。

span.span: Defines and creates generic type parameters for dynamically defined generic types and methods.

summary.span: 此类不能被继承。

span.span: This class cannot be inherited.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 可以获取的数组通过使用对象方法将类型参数添加到动态类型，从而使其泛型类型，或使用方法将类型参数添加到动态方法。You can get an array of objects by using the method to add type parameters to a dynamic type, thus making it a generic type, or by using the method to add type parameters to a dynamic method. 使用要将约束添加到类型参数的对象。Use the objects to add constraints to the type parameters. 约束有三种：Constraints are of three kinds: - 基类型约束指定泛型类型参数分配任何类型必须从特定的基类型派生。The base type constraint specifies that any type assigned to the generic type parameter must derive from a particular base type. 通过设置此约束方法。Set this constraint by using the method. - 接口约束指定泛型类型参数分配任何类型必须实现特定接口。An interface constraint specifies that any type assigned to the generic type parameter must implement a particular interface. 通过设置接口约束方法。Set the interface constraints by using the method. - 特殊约束指定任何类型分配给泛型类型参数必须具有默认构造函数，必须是引用类型，或者必须是值类型。Special constraints specify that any type assigned to the generic type parameter must have a default constructor, must be a reference type, or must be a value type. 使用设置为类型参数的特殊约束方法。Set the special constraints for a type parameter by using the method. 不能使用的方法检索到接口约束和特殊约束类。Interface constraints and special constraints cannot be retrieved using methods of the class. 创建包含的类型参数的泛型类型后，可以使用其对象以反映约束。Once you have created the generic type that contains the type parameters, you can use its object to reflect the constraints. 使用方法以获取类型参数，并为每个类型参数使用方法以获取该基类型约束和接口约束和要获取的特殊约束属性。Use the method to get the type parameters, and for each type parameter use the method to get the base type constraint and interface constraints, and the property to get the special constraints. ## Examples 下面的代码示例使用两个类型参数，创建一个泛型类型，并将它们保存在程序集 GenericEmitExample1.dll。The following code example creates a generic type with two type parameters, and saves them in the assembly GenericEmitExample1.dll. 可以使用[Ildasm.exe （IL 反汇编程序）](~/docs/framework/tools/ildasm-exe-il-disassembler.md)若要查看生成的类型。You can use the [Ildasm.exe (IL Disassembler)](~/docs/framework/tools/ildasm-exe-il-disassembler.md) to view the generated types. 定义动态的泛型类型中涉及的步骤的更多详细说明，请参阅[如何： 用反射发出泛型类型定义](~/docs/framework/reflection-and-codedom/how-to-define-a-generic-type-with-reflection-emit.md)。For a more detailed explanation of the steps involved in defining a dynamic generic type, see [How to: Define a Generic Type with Reflection Emit](~/docs/framework/reflection-and-codedom/how-to-define-a-generic-type-with-reflection-emit.md). remarks.format: ## Remarks 方法提供了一种方法生成参数列表的数组类型。The method provides a way to generate array types for parameter lists. ## Examples 下面的代码示例创建一个动态模块、 名为抽象的泛型类型`Sample`使用一个类型参数`T`，和一个名为的抽象方法`TestMethod`。The following code example creates a dynamic module, an abstract generic type named `Sample` with one type parameter, `T`, and an abstract method named `TestMethod`. `TestMethod` 采用`ref`参数 (`ByRef`在 Visual Basic 中) 的类型`T`，指向类型的指针`T`，和一个数组`T`。`TestMethod` takes a `ref` parameter (`ByRef` in Visual Basic) of type `T`, a pointer to type `T`, and an array of `T`. 此方法返回的二维数组`T`。This method returns a two-dimensional array of `T`. 代码示例将动态模块保存到磁盘，以便你可以使用 MSIL 反汇编程序 (Ildasm.exe) 对其进行检查。The code example saves the dynamic module to disk, so you can examine it using the MSIL Disassembler (Ildasm.exe). remarks.format: ## Remarks 若要检索的基类型约束使用属性。To retrieve the base type constraint use the property. 创建包含类型参数的泛型类型后，可以使用其对象以反映类型参数和它们的约束。Once you have created the generic type that contains the type parameter, you can use its object to reflect the type parameter and their constraints. 若要获取完整的泛型类型的类型参数，请使用方法。To get the type parameters of a completed generic type, use the method. 对于每个类型参数，获取基类型约束和接口约束通过使用方法，并使用获取的特殊约束属性。For each type parameter, get the base type constraint and interface constraints by using the method, and get the special constraints by using the property. ## Examples 下面的代码示例使用两个类型参数，第二个具有基类型约束，并将其保存在程序集中 GenericEmitExample1.dll 创建泛型类型。The following code example creates a generic type with two type parameters, the second of which has a base type constraint, and saves them in the assembly GenericEmitExample1.dll. 可以使用[Ildasm.exe （IL 反汇编程序）](~/docs/framework/tools/ildasm-exe-il-disassembler.md)若要查看生成的类型。You can use the [Ildasm.exe (IL Disassembler)](~/docs/framework/tools/ildasm-exe-il-disassembler.md) to view the generated types. 定义动态的泛型类型中涉及的步骤的更多详细说明，请参阅[如何： 用反射发出泛型类型定义](~/docs/framework/reflection-and-codedom/how-to-define-a-generic-type-with-reflection-emit.md)。For a more detailed explanation of the steps involved in defining a dynamic generic type, see [How to: Define a Generic Type with Reflection Emit](~/docs/framework/reflection-and-codedom/how-to-define-a-generic-type-with-reflection-emit.md). span.span: Sets the variance characteristics and special constraints of the generic parameter, such as the parameterless constructor constraint.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 特殊约束可以指定任何类型分配给泛型类型参数必须具有默认构造函数，必须是引用类型，或者必须是值类型。Special constraints can specify that any type assigned to the generic type parameter must have a default constructor, must be a reference type, or must be a value type. 不能使用的方法检索特殊约束类。Special constraints cannot be retrieved using methods of the class. 创建包含类型参数的泛型类型后，可以使用其对象以反映的类型参数和它们的约束。Once you have created the generic type that contains the type parameter, you can use its object to reflect the type parameters and their constraints. 若要获取完整的泛型类型的类型参数，请使用方法。To get the type parameters of a completed generic type, use the method. 若要获取的每个类型形参的特殊约束，请使用属性。To get the special constraints for each type parameter, use the property. 引用类型参数的方差特征的枚举值是只适用于支持协变和逆变，如 Microsoft 中间语言 (MSIL) 的语言。The enumeration values that refer to the variance characteristics of a type parameter are relevant only in languages that support covariance and contravariance, such as Microsoft intermediate language (MSIL). Visual Basic 和 C# 当前不支持协变和逆变。Visual Basic and C# currently do not support covariance and contravariance. ## Examples 下面的代码示例使用两个类型参数，其中第一个约束具有默认构造函数，并且是引用类型，并将其保存在程序集中 GenericEmitExample1.dll 创建泛型类型。The following code example creates a generic type with two type parameters, the first of which is constrained to have a default constructor and to be a reference type, and saves them in the assembly GenericEmitExample1.dll. 可以使用[Ildasm.exe （IL 反汇编程序）](~/docs/framework/tools/ildasm-exe-il-disassembler.md)若要查看生成的类型。You can use the [Ildasm.exe (IL Disassembler)](~/docs/framework/tools/ildasm-exe-il-disassembler.md) to view the generated types. 定义动态的泛型类型中涉及的步骤的更多详细说明，请参阅[如何： 用反射发出泛型类型定义](~/docs/framework/reflection-and-codedom/how-to-define-a-generic-type-with-reflection-emit.md)。For a more detailed explanation of the steps involved in defining a dynamic generic type, see [How to: Define a Generic Type with Reflection Emit](~/docs/framework/reflection-and-codedom/how-to-define-a-generic-type-with-reflection-emit.md).
